name: Vibrant Varanasi
description: Varanasi / Banaras is one of the oldest living cities in the world. Banaras is older than history. It is the ultimate pilgrimage spot for Hindus. Thousands visit Varanasi every day as a part of their religious beliefs. But, here I am documenting the touristy side of Varanasi. Here is a woman taking a dip in the Ganges for a cool photo.
